cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with scene understanding and semantic segmentation from geometric cues. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper aims to bring semantic segmentation in the loop of real-time reconstruction, which is relevant to robotics. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper uses a deep autoencoder stack for semantic segmentation. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper deals with automated scene understanding. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is less likely but still possible as the paper uses a novel 3D scene library for generating synthetic depth data.
